<!-- wp:heading {"align":"left","level":1,"textColor":"accent"} -->
<h1 class="has-accent-color has-text-color has-text-align-left">About</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>In the light of JumpStart Pakistan’s vision to ignite an economic revolution, the primary hurdle to initiate the change process on a National scale is Pakistan’s deteriorating image among the Global Investors especially the Overseas Pakistanis. In order to support the Entrepreneurial activities in Pakistan, we need to win back the confidence of Overseas Pakistanis and other Global financial players by inviting them to visit Pakistan and showcasing our Startups that provide the investment opportunity in unique and contemporary ideas, the SMEs that are already producing revenue and creating jobs and have the potential to become the Enterprise Corporations as well as Universities that are focused on harnessing the human resource that feed the Startups, SMEs as well as Enterprise Corporations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"align":"left","level":1,"textColor":"accent"} -->
<h1 class="has-accent-color has-text-color has-text-align-left">Idea</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>L.I.F.T Pakistan Conference is a platform designed specifically for showcasing Pakistan’s true assets i.e. Startups, SMEs and Universities that shape up the Entrepreneurial Eco System. We will bring together the most innovative Pakistani Startups with their Founders, the most successful Pakistani SMEs that have a proven market and financial track record and have the potential to increase their revenue manifold with the right exposure and resources, the HEC recognized and highly rated Universities along with their faculty, students, research professionals and management, the Pakistani Investors who have been investing with Startups and their case studies, the Overseas Pakistanis to play their key role in this movement, the Global Financial players to explore Pakistan as a safe market for their future investments and the Government officials of 80+ countries to witness Pakistan’s potential in becoming the next Economic Power in the Global arena.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

